### VLab — Cron Tasks API Tests
### Covers: task list, toggle
### Run: npm run dev (port 8800)

@base = http://localhost:8800
@api  = {{base}}/api

@adminEmail    = admin@vlab.com
@adminPassword = admin123


###
# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login — admin
POST {{api}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}


###
# ============================================================
# CRON TASKS
# ============================================================

### List all tasks and their state
GET {{api}}/cron/tasks

###

### Toggle task: shutdown-vms (每天22:00关机)
POST {{api}}/cron/tasks/shutdown-vms/toggle
